  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WalkBot</strong> is a quirky story-driven puzzle game set in a silly future - told over three exciting acts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062630/extras/af2eb824d219aff79f5c06369fdae4d5.poster.avif?t=1744109746\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062630/extras/af2eb824d219aff79f5c06369fdae4d5.webm?t=1744109746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062630/extras/af2eb824d219aff79f5c06369fdae4d5.mp4?t=1744109746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>WalkBot</strong>, you play as a new prototype of the product line \"WalkBot.\" You have one purpose: to walk. Unlike other types of bots, WalkBots lack any special abilities (except for, of course, walking). Luckily, though, the head is detachable and can be attached to all types of machinery within the lab. <strong>So launch your head to move ahead!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062630/extras/286490d4225f88f4ee1977fb7f949267.poster.avif?t=1744109746\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062630/extras/286490d4225f88f4ee1977fb7f949267.webm?t=1744109746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062630/extras/286490d4225f88f4ee1977fb7f949267.mp4?t=1744109746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WalkBot</strong> is a quirky story-driven puzzle game set in a silly future - told over three exciting acts. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062630/extras/af2eb824d219aff79f5c06369fdae4d5.poster.avif?t=1744109746\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062630/extras/af2eb824d219aff79f5c06369fdae4d5.webm?t=1744109746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062630/extras/af2eb824d219aff79f5c06369fdae4d5.mp4?t=1744109746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>WalkBot</strong>, you play as a new prototype of the product line \"WalkBot.\" You have one purpose: to walk. Unlike other types of bots, WalkBots lack any special abilities (except for, of course, walking). Luckily, though, the head is detachable and can be attached to all types of machinery within the lab. <strong>So launch your head to move ahead!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062630/extras/286490d4225f88f4ee1977fb7f949267.poster.avif?t=1744109746\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062630/extras/286490d4225f88f4ee1977fb7f949267.webm?t=1744109746\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2062630/extras/286490d4225f88f4ee1977fb7f949267.mp4?t=1744109746\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
